      <hedline>
        <hl1>MANAGEMENT SHAKE-UP AT VARIG</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Jennifer L. Rich</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Rich, Jennifer L</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Osires Silva is named president of Varig Airlines, replacing Fernando Pinto (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Brazil's largest airline, Varig, replaced its president in a shake-up intended to return the carrier to profitability. It has lost money in three of the past four years. The new president, Osires Silva, a member of Varig's board, replaced Fernando Pinto, who cut costs and jobs. The carrier still lost $54 million last year.</p>
        <p>Jennifer L. Rich</p>
      </block>
